<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.6">
<l>naivāya vemmēpō ṉāṇmatiyē nīyinnāṇ</l>
<l>maivā ṉiruḷakaṟṟāy māḻāntutēmputiyā</l>
<l>laivā yaravaṇaimē lāḻipperumāṉār</l>
<l>meyvāca kaṅkēṭṭuṉ meynnīrmai tōṟṟāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who waste away just like us, [one-]day moon! You who do not dispell</l>
<l>the darkness of the kajal sky today, let you become dim [and] fade,</l>
<l>you who, after hearing as true the words of the great lord with the discus on</l>
<l>the five-mouthed serpent’s bed, you show your true nature.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
